{"tid":181910,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"容祖兒演唱會","createTime":"2017-04-01T03:09:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-01T03:20:37.000Z","uid":431,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0185394cb14ec6a16747fe1a80ccede2c708af51","tid":181910,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T03:09:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JTcdgHhMNCU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJTcdgHhMNCU&d=rH9paZ2ORyePGAAUSKfbjRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=4f150e8d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JTcdgHhMNCU</a><br />\n<br />\n期待著和你　經歷最好時光　可以嗎<br />\n還有逗留在耳邊的說話<br />\n期待著和你　覆述愛的神話　聽見嗎<br />\n能為你　將一生都可以花<br />\n<br />\n期待屬於你　今後美好時光　可以嗎<br />\n還會　共鳴未說出的說話<br />\n期待屬於你　今後愛的豐收　可以嗎<br />\n能為你將一生都可以花<br />\n未來　同渡變化"},{"pid":"bad4e2fff0ec0628aeb3845f207f46e066349b13","tid":181910,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T03:10:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8Vk9MZNJE6E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D8Vk9MZNJE6E&d=rH9paZ2ORyePGAAUSKfbjRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=abc85592\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8Vk9MZNJE6E</a><br />\n<br />\n傷我或是害我都慘不過　教我記得一起幸福過<br />\n情願我聽不清楚　當時誰人口口聲聲不會掉低我<br />\n待我差我沒有奈何　為何扮好心慰問很掛念我麼<br />\n還能成為密友麼　你說得真輕鬆<br />\n講笑也　別太過"},{"pid":"e564d8ddefb1308e995c80237943c4171acd537f","tid":181910,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T03:10:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E4jPiazznkY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DE4jPiazznkY&d=rH9paZ2ORyePGAAUSKfbjRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=b5787350\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E4jPiazznkY</a><br />\n<br />\n由這一分鐘 開始計起 春風秋雨間<br />\n限我對你以 半年時間 慢慢的心淡<br />\n付清帳單 平靜的對你熱度褪減<br />\n一天一點 傷心過這 一百數十晚<br />\n大概也夠我送我來回地獄又折返人~間~~<br />\n春天分手 秋天會習慣<br />\n苦沖開了便淡"},{"pid":"ab85dc9efca7251d8d6daf1225fe042cd9f69755","tid":181910,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T03:11:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3KgUtQW4X_8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3KgUtQW4X_8&d=rH9paZ2ORyePGAAUSKfbjRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=1aa27d7c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3KgUtQW4X_8</a><br />\n<br />\n陪著你你都不會知<br />\n凝視你背影一輩子<br />\n旁人常在笑我堅持<br />\n我只得堅持<br />\n我喜歡堅持<br />\n即使只相隔著塊纸<br />\n相親必須同時同意<br />\n地上最遠的只怕是　同場<br />\n也不看我一次<br />\n牆紙一般貼在門牆是我<br />\n填充畫面那內容　無權伴你躺臥<br />\n想知這角碎花<br />\n只裝飾你的　堂皇神殿麼<br />\n可曾被你欣賞過<br />\n其實我也想講你知<br />\n誰伴你也非一輩子<br />\n來年來月我褪色時<br />\n你想珍惜時<br />\n後悔都很遲<br />\n只擔心撕去這塊紙<br />\n空出一方無人留意<br />\n沒若有所失的你　未懷疑<br />\n美景缺了一處<br />\n牆紙一般貼在門牆是我<br />\n填充畫面那內容　無權伴你躺臥<br />\n想知這角碎花<br />\n只裝飾你的　堂皇神殿麼<br />\n可曾被你欣賞過<br />\n牆紙一般盼待情人路過<br />\n從此安守你後台　無缘為你闖禍<br />\n想知一旦有天<br />\n壁花都已枯　情人懷念麼<br />\n可曾為我傷心過"},{"pid":"4d92e47a7afceb3bb53321d729873eb46007d60b","tid":181910,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T03:11:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S9oonBJeoRE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DS9oonBJeoRE&d=rH9paZ2ORyePGAAUSKfbjRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=42918ff0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S9oonBJeoRE</a><br />\n<br />\n聽笑話　盡量笑得不勉強<br />\n我望鏡　愁雲密佈我面上<br />\n皺著眉　旁人問我何解這樣<br />\n在這　愉快的現場"},{"pid":"e1c60e0923938773d1b5bbe6de13647467a8dcad","tid":181910,"uid":35105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T03:12:10.000Z","msg":"幫我"},{"pid":"381cb82e3fb62324b95eda35f11fc9101a3edd18","tid":181910,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T03:12:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8ejA5NcuC0Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D8ejA5NcuC0Q&d=rH9paZ2ORyePGAAUSKfbjRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=c91231e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8ejA5NcuC0Q</a><br />\n<br />\n留戀不需要哭　<br />\n需要一首怨曲<br />\n玫瑰花需要交代　<br />\n未來的祝福<br />\n想親歷多一次　<br />\n寫不完的故事<br />\n是時候了一一<br />\n關進了這空間"},{"pid":"20d8693402e44ade73fc31655852ba13b282405d","tid":181910,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T03:12:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幫我</blockquote><br />\n我係死忠"},{"pid":"91f0eaeff330f2e4f51f168026c45fc5c89b830c","tid":181910,"uid":35105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T03:13:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>幫我</blockquote><br />\n我係死忠</blockquote><br />\n勁<br />\n有冇睇演唱會"},{"pid":"f09c20387bc99e97afda4bf87ab3988b62b84258","tid":181910,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T03:13:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6fL56T5gu7Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6fL56T5gu7Q&d=rH9paZ2ORyePGAAUSKfbjRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=b1178813\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6fL56T5gu7Q</a><br />\n<br />\n沒有人懲罰我 完全是我 難平復淒楚<br />\n憑空的塑造出幾千個<br />\n徘徊著 未散的 靈魂在共我拍拖<br />\n那些追憶 本可一躍就過<br />\n我偏喜歡給它一再折磨<br />\n其實滿懷執著 不甘心的一個是我"},{"pid":"6feb0206d64de6f9301830b07702c44c87e41553","tid":181910,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T03:13:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YUJObfMtq7c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYUJObfMtq7c&d=rH9paZ2ORyePGAAUSKfbjRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=42acf74c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YUJObfMtq7c</a>"},{"pid":"5a4cbb640c7fd138db7e308007f4a9ae1b2179c7","tid":181910,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T03:13:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xIhk1HCh2Oc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.l